category: Libs
requires: cygwin libGL1 libGLU1 libphysfs1 libpng14 libSDL1.2_0 libSDL_sound1.0_1 lua
external-source: radius-engine
sdesc: "Lua based real-time 2D graphics game engine (runtime)"
ldesc: "Radius Engine is a Lua script-based real-time 2D graphics engine
designed for rapidly prototyping games. Built on top of SDL and OpenGL, games
made with Radius Engine are portable to both Windows and Linux."
